title: OOPSDOGGY Reflective Geniune Leather Dog Collar Soft Padded Collars for Small Medium Large Breed Dogs Puppy, 4 Sizes, 8 Colors (Camel, 12"-15")
features: SIZE: Our carefully crafted soft padded medium leather dog collar is specifically created to suit dogs with a neck size ranging from 30cm to 38cm. Prior to completing your purchase, we highly advise utilizing a gentle measuring tape to precisely measure your dog's neck circumference, ensuring an ideal fit.

MATERIAL: Our handcrafted leather dog collars are made from authentic leather and feature a sturdy metal buckle and D-ring. Each collar is enhanced with unique reflective threads, promoting increased visibility for added safety during nighttime. When selecting a dog collar, durability is crucial due to the everyday wear and tear it undergoes.

COLORS: Our leather puppy collars are offered in eight lively colors: Black, Blue, Brown, Camel, Denim, Green, Pink, and Red. This diverse range enables you to select the ideal shade that complements your dog's personality and style.

COMFORT: Leather, being a natural material, offers breathability and is less likely to cause irritation to your dog. The padding ensures comfort around the neck, making it ideal for dogs that tend to pull during walks. The robust stitching guarantees strength, alleviating any concerns about potential breakage.

CARE SUGGESTIONS: To preserve the quality and durability of your leather products, it is recommended to avoid exposure to moisture. Opt for dry cleaning methods to ensure your collar remains in optimal condition for an extended period.
